\'93Yes.\'94 said Miles, still stunned, \'93Yes I see now.\'94\
Toby, keen to give poor Miles a break, picked the map up off the floor. \'93talk us through it June?\'94\
\'93Hold on.\'94 said Phillip, who had been quiet the whole time. \'93What about me? I spent five days in hospital sick as a dog to get that bleeding map, I think I have earned the right to come along too.\'94\
